     * context. Note that vacuous changes &mdash; e.g. foo.setName(foo.getName()
     * &mdash; will not trip the changed flag. Similarly, "unmaking" a change will
     * clear the isChanged flag
     * 
     * <pre>
     * String name = bar.getName();
